citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50 am on 01-
NOV-23.
Arrived at the gate 10:50 am and called licensee. I waited for a call back. Call back received at 11:14 am. Licensee stated
not available. Asked for a call back when licensee returned for possible inspection. Call back received at 4:50 pm too late
for inspection.
End Section
